  <Description GUID="f9b16eb3-5b1a-4856-9189-6e2726348dcb">
    <div GUID="ada39556-c83c-4cfc-bf1a-381bac3ec84b" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">This lesson will teach you about the general duties and restrictions imposed on all individuals and companies under the RMA.</div>
    <div GUID="4b7517cd-e4fa-4306-86e6-418485c1dc51" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"> </div>
    <div GUID="1b949ad9-5858-4d9d-a685-04155b3762c1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">You should complete the lesson in about <strong GUID="e76c9ad7-2494-48e5-bdfe-f795b737591d">15 minutes</strong>. </div>
    <div GUID="89fab7e3-ac43-48b2-8a57-483ecd075df1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"> </div>
    <div GUID="9a9135f7-e316-4538-820b-a6e9ba7c8d8c" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">At the end of the lesson you should have a clear understanding of:</div>
    <div GUID="3b1c44f5-3654-4888-80d8-95b4983d66ec" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"> </div>
    <ul style="MARGIN-TOP: 0px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px" type="disc" GUID="a8c737ae-d933-47a1-921e-e7b6eef2342a" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
