      <Title GUID="a0e783f9-6815-43c9-b58f-2a0f285fc858">Hypothetical situation</Title>
      <PageElements GUID="a89b2a90-e163-455e-b135-d665525b2719">
        <PageElement GUID="78260d0d-30d3-4cac-87e4-ffd61226190c">
          <Graphic GUID="354cb79d-4c69-474a-b202-2b9d0083a936"> <![CDATA[<div class="Graphic_Main">
  <img src="Images/7cf56b7b-bf1c-4bf0-92e3-ba749d5faa24.gif" alt="" align="texttop">
</div>]]></Graphic>
        </PageElement>
        <PageElement GUID="29ac1159-8c6b-4c40-9df1-2a59acc9ac1c">
          <TextBox GUID="0043341f-603d-45e6-a339-67b7febf6554"> <![CDATA[<div class="TextBox_Main">
  <Description GUID="8a488941-2d4d-4091-9ee1-a509e6671a58">
    <div GUID="cc0a796f-fd5c-49c7-b41b-9cfe0e5ac1cb" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">A mining company operates a gold mine. The mining operation uses cyanide to obtain gold from the ore. The waste ('tailings') generated by the processing operation contain cyanide, high concentrations of salt and other heavy metals. The contaminated tailings are piped from the processing plant to a large holding dam.  <br GUID="72d5c45b-90dd-43eb-bb39-5c86ec4c9cc5"> <br GUID="b1ac3647-a1a8-4895-8084-e27c2c577090">The mining company holds all necessary approvals for the mining operation, including a permit which authorises it to hold the tailings in the dam. The permit states that all runoff must be contained within the mine’s operational areas.<br GUID="d397ef38-ce09-459f-8ecc-1504c27875d2"> <br GUID="90939713-d541-477c-b696-a94fb722c475">Over a period of about a week there is a lot of heavy rain. The tailings dam is already holding more than its 75% design capacity. The dam overflows, and the tailings flow into a nearby creek, and then into a lake, killing fish and other wildlife.  There is no secondary (additional reinforcement) bunding around the dam to contain the overflow.</div>
    <div GUID="b812162f-40dd-4586-9652-a833e0a0e0b9" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"> </div>
    <div GUID="45354a80-be09-45ed-8c9e-4ac2ca8bdbb1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
      <strong GUID="ea9d9ce5-5635-444c-b2dd-e81b96cf3d9f">Consider this scenario while reading the next pages...</strong>
    </div>
  </Description>
</div>]]></TextBox>
